low-cost VR experiences

00:02:16.160 --> 00:02:19.130
live comfortably on the
near side of the VR valley.

00:02:19.130 --> 00:02:21.060
These experiences
aren't cut-down versions

00:02:21.060 --> 00:02:21.966
of high-grade VR.

00:02:21.966 --> 00:02:23.340
They're just their
own experience

00:02:23.340 --> 00:02:26.400
that has a different kind
of set of affordances.

00:02:26.400 --> 00:02:31.360
