00:02:40.170 --> 00:02:42.700
And she's also holding
her hands up to her face,

00:02:42.700 --> 00:02:44.340
which gives her this
feeling like she's

00:02:44.340 --> 00:02:45.710
peering into something.

00:02:45.710 --> 00:02:48.240
