a very different experience

00:02:48.240 --> 00:02:50.040
than feeling like
you're teleporting.

00:02:50.040 --> 00:02:52.290
It's like you're looking
into something, not replacing

00:02:52.290 --> 00:02:54.410
your entire sensory
field, like an SLR camera

00:02:54.410 --> 00:02:57.960
or, say, this 1861
megalethoscope that I

00:02:57.960 --> 00:03:01.510
found in a Stanford museum.

00:03:01.510 --> 00:03:04.040
