00:03:09.420 --> 00:03:12.374
So what we're calling
this is bit-sized VR.

00:03:12.374 --> 00:03:13.790
So let's take a
look at an example

00:03:13.790 --> 00:03:14.970
that you have right now.

00:03:14.970 --> 00:03:17.670
