00:04:20.230 --> 00:04:22.550
So imagine you're making
a first-person shooter.

00:04:22.550 --> 00:04:24.940
For an onlooker, you might
want to make an experience

00:04:24.940 --> 00:04:26.160
like being a security camera.

00:04:26.160 --> 00:04:27.546
You are in a stationary place.

00:04:27.546 --> 00:04:28.920
So your controls
are pretty easy,

00:04:28.920 --> 00:04:30.700
and you're just looking around
watching everybody shoot

00:04:30.700 --> 00:04:31.520
at each other.

00:04:31.520 --> 00:04:33.255
I think that's
going to be awesome.

00:04:33.255 --> 00:04:34.630
Another thing is
if you're making

00:04:34.630 --> 00:04:37.300
